jcr:content.jcr:title: Brownie Badge Workshop, Investigation - Senses (SOLD OUT)

data.details:
Scouts will come to their senses in this multi-disciplinary workshop that teaches the biology of the five senses through hands-on science experiments. This workshop will help the scouts understand the difference between their five senses. This event costs $12 per girl.

This event has been sold out.
